'''安培'''（{{lang-en|ampere}}，{{lang-fr|ampère}}）简称'''安'''（amp），是[[电流强度|电流强度]]的[[单位_(度量衡)|单位]]，[[国际单位制|国际单位制]]七个[[國際單位制基本單位|基本单位]]之一<ref group= "注">另外六个是[[米_(单位)|米]]、[[开尔文|开尔文]]、[[秒|秒]]、[[摩尔_(单位)|摩尔]]、[[坎德拉|坎德拉]]和[[千克|千克]]</ref>，符号 '''A'''<ref>{{cite book|author=张三慧|title=大学物理学·电磁学|year=1999|publisher=清华大学出版社|location=北京|isbn=9787302038191|pages=143}}</ref><ref name="BIPMdefinition">{{Citation|chapter= 2.1. Unit of electric current (ampere)|url= http://www.bipm.org/en/si/si_brochure/chapter2/2-1/ampere.html|title= SI brochure|edition= 8th|publisher= BIPM|accessdate= 19 November 2011|archive-date= 2012-02-03|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20120203153904/http://www.bipm.org/en/si/si_brochure/chapter2/2-1/ampere.html|dead-url= yes}}</ref><ref>[http://physics.nist.gov/cuu/Units/ampere.html Base unit definitions: Ampere] {{Wayback|url=http://physics.nist.gov/cuu/Units/ampere.html |date=20170425134625 }}. Physics.nist.gov. Retrieved on 2010-09-28.</ref>。安培是以[[法国|法国]][[数学|数学]]家和[[物理|物理]]学家[[安德烈-马里·安培|安德烈-马里·安培]]命名的，为了纪念他在[[经典电磁学|经典电磁学]]方面的贡献。

实际情况中，安培是对单位[[时间|时间]]内通过[[导体|导体]]横截面的[[电荷量|电荷量]]的度量。1[[秒|秒]]内通过横截面的[[电荷量|电荷量]]为 1[[库仑|库仑]]（{{val|6.241|e=18}}个电子的电荷量）时，电流强度為 1安培<ref>{{Citation|last=Bodanis|first=David|year=2005|title=Electric Universe|place=New York|publisher= Three Rivers Press|ISBN=978-0-307-33598-2}}</ref>。1安培也相当于 1伏特电压施加在 1欧姆[[阻抗|阻抗]]时，所通过的[[电流量|电流量]]（电流强度）。

比一安培小的電流可以用[[毫安|毫安]]、[[微安|微安]]等[[計量單位|單位]]表示。
* 1安（A）= 1000毫安（mA）
* 1毫安（mA）= 1000微安（μA）

== 定义 ==
[[File:Unit_relations_in_the_new_SI.svg|缩略图]]和由同一组常数定义的其他基本单位。]]

2018年11月16日，第26届国际计量大会决定，重新定义安培为：{{Cquote|[[安培|安培]]，符号 A，为 SI 的电流单位。当[[基本电荷|基本电荷]] {{mvar|e}}，以单位 [[库仑|C]]（即 A·s）表示时，将其固定数值取为 {{val|1.602176634|e=-19}} 来定义安培，其中[[秒|秒]]用 {{math|Δ''ν''<sub>Cs</sub>}} 定义。<ref name= "nim.ac">{{cite web|url=http://www.nim.ac.cn/sites/www.nim.ac.cn/files/news2018/10-12/Resolution%201.pdf|publisher=中国计量科学研究院|title=大会决议中文版|accessdate=2019-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190204174438/http://www.nim.ac.cn/sites/www.nim.ac.cn/files/news2018/10-12/Resolution%201.pdf|archive-date=2019-02-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>}}

其中 {{math|Δ''ν''<sub>Cs</sub>}} 是指[[铯|铯]]133原子基态的两个超精细能级之间的跃迁辐射频率。新定义使用基本电荷 e 重新定义安培，这样的条件可以在实验室中重现，同时较简单易明，于2019年5月20日生效（[[2019年國際單位制基本單位重新定義|2019年國際單位制基本單位重新定義]]）。

== 历史 ==
安培最初是被定义为[[厘米-克-秒制|厘米-克-秒制]]中电流单位[[绝对安培|绝对安培]]的十分之一<ref>{{Citation | url = http://alpha.montclair.edu/~kowalskiL/SI/SI_PAGE.HTML | title = A short history of the SI units in electricity | publisher = Montclair | last = Kowalski | first = L | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090429035624/http://alpha.montclair.edu/~kowalskiL/SI/SI_PAGE.HTML | archivedate = 2009-04-29 | accessdate = 2014-11-21 }}.</ref>。如此确定它的大小是为了保证从[[国际单位制|国际单位制]]中的其他单位推导安培得到的值比较合适。<!--这句翻译仍需改良，原文：The size of the unit was chosen so that the units derived from it in the [[International_System_of_Unit|International System of Unit]] would be conveniently sized.-->

“国际安培”是一个较早的电流单位，定义为使[[硝酸银|硝酸银]]溶液中每秒析出 {{val|fmt=commas|0.001118000}}克[[银|银]]的电流<ref>{{Citation | url = http://www.sizes.com/units/ampHist.htm | title = History of the ampere | publisher = Sizes | accessdate = 2014-11-21 | archive-date = 2016-10-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161020170913/http://sizes.com/units/ampHist.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。之后，更精确地测量发现，这一电流是 0.99985 A。

1948年第九届国际计量大会决定定义安培为：{{Cquote|真空中，截面积可忽略的两根相距 1米的无限长平行圆直导线内，通以等量恒定电流时，若导线间相互作用在每[[米_(单位)|米]]长度上的力为 2×10<sup>–7</sup> [[牛顿_(单位)|牛顿]]，则每根导线中的电流为一安培。| <ref name= "BIPMdefinition" /><ref>{{Citation | first = Paul MS | last = Monk | title = Physical Chemistry: Understanding our Chemical World | publisher = John Wiley & Sons | year = 2004 | ISBN = 0-471-49180-2 | url = http://books.google.com/books?vid=ISBN0471491802&id=LupAi35QjhoC&pg=PA16&lpg=PA16&ots=IMiGyIL-67&dq=ampere+definition+si&sig=9Y0k0wgvymmLNYFMcXodwJZwvAM}}.</ref>}}

2005年，[[国际计量委员会|国际计量委员会]]同意研究将元电荷电荷量用于安培定义的可能。新的定义在2014年的第25屆[[国际度量衡委员会|国际度量衡委员会]]上被討論，于2019年5月20日生效。<ref>{{cite press release
| url = http://www.bipm.org/utils/en/pdf/Press_release_resolution_1_CGPM.pdf
| title = General Conference on Weights and Measures approves possible changes to the International System of Units, including redefinition of the kilogram.
| publisher = General Conference on Weights and Measures
| location = Sèvres, France
| date = 23 October 2011
| accessdate = 25 October 2011
| archive-date = 2012-02-09
| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120209175127/http://www.bipm.org/utils/en/pdf/Press_release_resolution_1_CGPM.pdf
| dead-url = no
}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nist.gov/news-events/news/2018/11/historic-vote-ties-kilogram-and-other-units-natural-constants|title=Historic Vote Ties Kilogram and Other Units to Natural Constants|publisher=NIST|language=en|date=2018-11-16|access-date=2018-11-16|archive-date=2019-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190529224841/https://www.nist.gov/news-events/news/2018/11/historic-vote-ties-kilogram-and-other-units-natural-constants|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2018年第二十六届国际计量大会通过给予[[元电荷|元电荷]]确定的电荷量，确定了安培的新定义。自2019年5月20日起，元电荷的电荷量被确定为 <math>1.602 176 634\times 10^{-19} C</math> ，而 <math> C = A \cdot s </math>。由此，1 安培所代表的电流强度大小由元电荷电荷量和秒确定。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.bipm.org/utils/common/pdf/CGPM-2018/26th-CGPM-Resolutions.pdf |title=Resolutions of the CGPM - 26th meeting of the CGPM: 13-16 November 2018 |access-date=2018-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181119214326/https://www.bipm.org/utils/common/pdf/CGPM-2018/26th-CGPM-Resolutions.pdf |archive-date=2018-11-19 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

== 应用 ==
安培这一单位与[[瓦特秤|瓦特秤]]和[[欧姆定律|欧姆定律]]中的单位[[伏特|伏特]]、[[欧姆|欧姆]]相联系。而在[[约瑟夫森效应|约瑟夫森效应]]和[[量子霍尔效应|量子霍尔效应]]中也都各自有所应用。<!--这一段需要改良，英语原文：The standard ampere is most accurately realized using a [[watt_balance|watt balance]], but is in practice maintained via [[Ohm's_law|Ohm's law]] from the units of [[electromotive_force|electromotive force]] and [[electrical_resistance|resistance]], the [[volt|volt]] and the [[ohm|ohm]], since the latter two can be tied to physical phenomena that are relatively easy to reproduce, the [[Josephson_junction|Josephson junction]] and the [[quantum_Hall_effect|quantum Hall effect]], respectively.--><ref name="Electrical quantities">{{Citation | url = http://www.bipm.org/en/si/si_brochure/appendix2/electrical.html | title = SI brochure | chapter = Appendix 2: Practical realization of unit definitions: Electrical quantities | publisher = BIPM | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090628091900/http://www.bipm.org/en/si/si_brochure/appendix2/electrical.html | archivedate = 2009-06-28 | accessdate = 2014-11-21 }}.</ref>

现在，建立一安培的技术已经能够达到10<sup>-7</sup>的[[逼近误差|逼近误差]]。<!--这一段需要改良，英语原文：At present, techniques to establish the realization of an ampere have a [[relative_uncertainty|relative uncertainty]] of approximately a few parts in 10<sup>7</sup>, and involve realizations of the watt, the ohm and the volt.--><ref name= "Electrical quantities" />

== 例子 ==
* 计算器工作电流 1×10<sup>-4</sup>A<ref group= "注">以CASIO fx-82ES 1.5V 0.0002W计</ref>
* 手机充电电流 0.5-2A （快充可到 5A以上)<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://graniteriverlabs.com.cn/article-pd-qc-introduction/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2022-04-04 |archive-date=2021-05-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210514101535/https://graniteriverlabs.com.cn/article-pd-qc-introduction/ }}</ref>
* 闪电约 1×10<sup>4</sup>A<ref>物理.高中二年级上册.上海科技出版社</ref>
* 住宅[[配電箱|配電箱]]約 60A
* 住宅[[斷路器|斷路器]]，常見的有 10/20A
* 塑殼斷路器（MCCB），常見 200-800A
* 空氣斷路器（ACB），用於低壓電（380V），常見 1600/2500/4000A
* 用於配電的 1650k[[VA|VA]][[三相|三相]][[變壓器|變壓器]]，低壓線圈（380V）最大輸出 2500A

